cast.name: 贝丝蒂·帕尔默 Betsy Palmer

this_title: Betsy Palmer: A Scream Queen Legend
introduction: Betsy Palmer does a one-on-one sit down interview - During this hour long conversation, she talks about her roles on Broadway and on television, starring in motion pictures like Mr. Roberts with Henry Fonda and Jack Lemmon, Queen Bee with Joan Crawford, Friday the 13th and her latest motion picture Bell Witch: The Movie.
chinese_title: Betsy Palmer: A Scream Queen Legend
